          <fr:mainmatter>
            <fr:p>After going to press, we have fixed the following mistakes:</fr:p>
            <fr:ol><fr:li>In the definition of a logos, we mistakenly said that "colimits commute with finite limits" but we meant to say that they are preserved by pullback. We thank <fr:link href="sarahzrf.xml" title="Sarah Z. Rovner-Frydman" addr="sarahzrf" type="local">Sarah Z. Rovner-Frydman</fr:link> for noticing this mistake.</fr:li>
  <fr:li>In Remark 5.15, we used the notation for the closed immersion prior to introducing it.</fr:li>
  <fr:li>We have fixed a few broken links in the bibliography.</fr:li></fr:ol>
            <fr:p>The local copy hosted here has the corrections implemented</fr:p>
